--  analysis of the orbit reduction strategy.
-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

-- The compat field is refl (S-cut is S-cut-rep ∘ classify100)
compat-is-trivial : (r : D100Region)
  → S-cut d100BdyView r ≡ S-cut-rep (classify100 r)
